1. Reg. 14. 2. Chron. 12. Shiſhak King of Aegypt came and rifled the Temple with the Kings Treaſure. ſo that he was forced to ſupply Solomons golden Shieldes, (which were then carried away) with the like of Braſſe. Thus he

