3. A.M. 3651 DEMETRIUS Poliorcetes, ſo called for his skill and ſucceſſe in ſubduing Citties. 2. He was a great help to his Father in moſt of his atchievements. 3. Coming himſelfe to raigne he paſſed Euphrates in the Eaſt, and ſubdued Babylon;
